items.title: JD Martinez smashes 40th home run
items.summary: By hitting a two-run homer to left-center field on Sunday afternoon at AT&T Park, D-backs outfielder J.D. Martinez became the third player in 2017 to reach 40 homers.
items.content: By hitting a two-run homer to left-center field on Sunday afternoon at AT&T Park, D-backs outfielder J.D. Martinez became the third player in 2017 to reach 40 homers.

items.title: Still no word on Arrieta's next step
items.summary: Jake Arrieta felt good after his bullpen session on Saturday, but the Cubs have yet to announce when the right-hander will return to the rotation.
